# Backend

- DTOs: `backend/src/common/dto/` · Guards: `backend/src/auth/guards/`
- `ComplianceService`: ACTIVE status for features; KYC gate for payouts only
- Signal Hub proxy + webhooks under `backend/src/signals/`
- AI: `backend/src/ai/` (vision, validation, support agent)
- MetaAPI broker layer: map synthetic symbols (e.g. VIX75 → 1HZ75V) before MT5 send
- Signal validation: reject structural issues (SL/TP side, entry zone) — not unfamiliar symbols
- Env secrets in `backend/.env` — never commit
